        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/www.wineberserkers.com/saul_mutchnick/{size}/940_2.png",
        "created_at": "2023-06-21T17:17:09.087Z",
        "cooked": "<p>You might want to reach out to Legend Imports, who now bring them into the US (<a href=\"https://legendaustralia.com/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">https://legendaustralia.com/</a>). They\u2019re a new-ish company (started during the pandemic by two American Master Somms who used to live in Melbourne), so they don\u2019t have fully national distribution (and obviously something like Giaconda is going to be very limited as it is)\u2014but they might be able to point you to the regional markets that get/will get an allocation.<br>\n[edited for typo]</p>",
